12
00:02:21,120 --> 00:02:21,640
Don't worry.

13
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:23,680
You'll see her soon.

14
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:28,200
I'm sure she'll like you

15
00:02:29,240 --> 00:02:30,800
