16
00:02:36,440 --> 00:02:37,840
Why haven't you

17
00:02:37,840 --> 00:02:39,120
mentioned her before?

18
00:02:39,520 --> 00:02:40,960
Should we prepare something

19
00:02:41,120 --> 00:02:42,960
