23
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:55,640
Did she seduce you?

24
00:02:56,600 --> 00:02:57,240
I told you.

25
00:02:57,240 --> 00:02:58,400
It has nothing to do with Zhen Yi.

26
00:02:59,120 --> 00:02:59,840
Even if it wasn't for her,

27
00:03:00,040 --> 00:03:00,920
we would have broken up anyway.

28
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:02,360
Don't leave me, okay?

29
00:03:02,840 --> 00:03:03,600
Let go.

30
00:03:04,360 --> 00:03:05,040
This money

31
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:06,200
should be enough for you to live for a while.

32
00:03:06,360 --> 00:03:06,920
Don't come looking for me.

33
00:03:07,440 --> 00:03:08,360
Don't cause me any trouble.

34
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:11,480
Mo Jiao is already thirteen years old.

35
00:03:12,040 --> 00:03:12,920
Can you really bear

36
00:03:12,920 --> 00:03:14,640
to let him grow up without a father?

37
00:03:25,840 --> 00:03:26,480
Mom,
will Dad come back?

38
00:03:30,480 --> 00:03:32,200
I'm sorry, baby.

39
00:03:34,600 --> 00:03:35,080
Huaiwang,

40
00:03:35,080 --> 00:03:36,840
