47
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:50,600
Jiao,

48
00:03:50,920 --> 00:03:52,040
Even you despise me?

49
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:53,680
Just like your dad,

50
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:56,400
