51
00:04:04,760 --> 00:04:05,240
Mom,

52
00:04:06,880 --> 00:04:07,840
get some sleep.

53
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:10,680
Once you fall asleep,
the pain will go away.

54
00:04:13,280 --> 00:04:13,920
Mom,

55
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:16,320
since you keep saying you love me,

56
00:04:16,760 --> 00:04:17,880
