59
00:05:26,320 --> 00:05:27,320
You're wrong.

60
00:05:28,680 --> 00:05:29,680
She committed suicide.

61
00:05:30,840 --> 00:05:32,200
She wanted to die.

62
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:34,160
What does it have to do with me?

63
00:05:49,160 --> 00:05:50,240
Where are you going?

64
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:05,680
You came here to see her, didn't you?

65
00:06:06,840 --> 00:06:08,720
I'll take you to see her now.

66
00:06:26,760 --> 00:06:27,960
This is my mom.

67
00:06:29,320 --> 00:06:30,520
Why are your eyes closed?

68
00:06:30,960 --> 00:06:32,160
Do you look down on my mom?

69
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:37,760
This is my dad.

70
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:39,680
When he died,

71
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:42,400
