72
00:06:46,880 --> 00:06:47,680
This...

73
00:06:49,720 --> 00:06:51,280
This is Lin Moqing's mother.

74
00:06:52,360 --> 00:06:53,920
I should thank her.

75
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:56,480
If it weren't for her and her son,

76
00:06:56,920 --> 00:06:58,880
I wouldn't be like this.

77
00:07:01,040 --> 00:07:01,840
You killed

78
00:07:03,320 --> 00:07:04,600
