79
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:09,800
Yes.

80
00:07:16,480 --> 00:07:17,280
Is this

81
00:07:19,640 --> 00:07:20,680
mine?

82
00:07:34,280 --> 00:07:35,640
Your acting is so bad.

83
00:07:36,720 --> 00:07:37,640
I should say,

84
00:07:38,760 --> 00:07:40,200
compared to Xu Meng,

85
00:07:44,320 --> 00:07:45,400
your acting is too poor.

86
00:07:46,640 --> 00:07:47,720
Only Xu Meng

87
00:07:49,400 --> 00:07:51,800
deserves the elaborate way of death I've designed.

88
00:07:51,960 --> 00:07:53,000
Don't hurt her.

89
00:07:53,320 --> 00:07:54,520
Don't hurt her.

90
00:07:57,920 --> 00:07:58,880
Don't hurt her.

91
00:08:00,960 --> 00:08:01,600
Beg me.

92
00:08:03,040 --> 00:08:03,720
I beg you.

93
00:08:04,440 --> 00:08:05,520
Please.

94
00:08:06,080 --> 00:08:07,480
Don't hurt her.

95
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:08,600
Please!

96
00:08:15,120 --> 00:08:16,840
Your parents were smart enough

97
00:08:18,040 --> 00:08:19,240
to leave a share transfer agreement

98
00:08:19,960 --> 00:08:21,280
