100
00:08:24,840 --> 00:08:25,640
Otherwise,

101
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:27,760
everything of Blue Crane

102
00:08:27,760 --> 00:08:29,840
will be donated to charity.

103
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:35,440
But they underestimated

104
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:36,520
how useless you are.

105
00:08:40,560 --> 00:08:41,360
Sign it!

106
00:08:42,800 --> 00:08:43,480
Sign it!

107
00:08:43,480 --> 00:08:45,720
and I might consider letting Xu Meng go.

108
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:05,000
If I'm in a good mood,

109
00:09:09,920 --> 00:09:12,120
I might let you two meet.

110
00:09:36,840 --> 00:09:37,720
Still no sign of Blue.

111
00:09:39,400 --> 00:09:40,600
Miss Xu's whereabouts.

112
00:09:41,320 --> 00:09:42,480
Let me take you home first.

113
00:10:12,360 --> 00:10:13,400
Where did you go?

114
00:10:13,880 --> 00:10:15,000
Do you know how worried I was

115
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:15,800
