127
00:11:06,960 --> 00:11:08,640
Until the moment I woke up.

128
00:11:14,560 --> 00:11:15,160
Mengmeng, listen to me.

129
00:11:15,560 --> 00:11:16,360
What do you want to say?

130
00:11:16,440 --> 00:11:17,640
Keep explaining.

131
00:11:17,880 --> 00:11:18,600
Listen to your lies.
I...

132
00:11:29,120 --> 00:11:30,800
Actually, the first time you woke up,

133
00:11:32,440 --> 00:11:33,840
