134
00:11:36,440 --> 00:11:38,000
We just rescued Lan Hewei,

135
00:11:39,360 --> 00:11:40,440
and Lin Mojiao came immediately.

136
00:11:42,600 --> 00:11:45,120
I didn't expect him to kill Lan Hewei so soon.

137
00:11:47,120 --> 00:11:48,280
By the time I got the message and arrived,

138
00:11:50,400 --> 00:11:52,000
you had suffered brain damage

139
00:11:52,320 --> 00:11:53,560
due to prolonged lack of oxygen,

140
00:11:54,400 --> 00:11:55,200
and lost your memory.

141
00:11:58,400 --> 00:11:59,640
The plan to have you impersonate Lan Hewei

142
00:12:00,360 --> 00:12:02,240
[to infiltrate the Lin family for revenge]

143
00:12:03,440 --> 00:12:04,720
[had to be terminated.]

144
00:12:05,840 --> 00:12:07,480
[After that, you regained consciousness several times,]

145
00:12:09,080 --> 00:12:10,120
[but then fell back into a coma.]

146
00:12:11,440 --> 00:12:12,680
[Your condition was very unstable.]

147
00:12:14,040 --> 00:12:14,800
Xu Meng.

148
00:12:17,600 --> 00:12:18,440
Xu Meng.

149
00:12:36,280 --> 00:12:36,680
Xu Meng.

150
00:12:38,240 --> 00:12:38,720
Cover your face.
Who are you?

151
00:12:41,640 --> 00:12:42,720
I am Mr. Zhen.

152
00:12:43,200 --> 00:12:44,200
Have you forgotten me?

153
00:12:47,160 --> 00:12:47,720
Don't worry,

154
00:12:48,400 --> 00:12:49,440
I won't hurt you.

155
00:12:49,720 --> 00:12:50,280
Trust me.

156
00:12:52,040 --> 00:12:52,480
Xu Meng.
Let me go.

157
00:12:53,360 --> 00:12:53,720
Let me go.
Xu Meng.

158
00:12:54,360 --> 00:12:55,080
Xu Meng.

159
00:13:12,640 --> 00:13:13,440
Where is this place?

160
00:13:15,040 --> 00:13:16,360
This is our home.

161
00:13:16,920 --> 00:13:17,520
Honey.

162
00:13:18,520 --> 00:13:19,680
I tried all sorts of methods

163
00:13:19,680 --> 00:13:20,640
to stimulate you,

164
00:13:21,440 --> 00:13:22,800
trying to help you recover your memory.

165
00:13:27,360 --> 00:13:29,600
Your mental state was very poor at that time.

166
00:13:30,040 --> 00:13:30,840
And

167
00:13:31,720 --> 00:13:33,440
if you go out with this face,

168
00:13:34,080 --> 00:13:35,360
you will easily be targeted by Lin Mojiao.

169
00:13:35,360 --> 00:13:36,600
That would be more dangerous for you.

170
00:13:37,400 --> 00:13:38,840
What about the resort project?

171
00:13:39,160 --> 00:13:41,320
I have already found the funding,

172
00:13:42,440 --> 00:13:44,720
