173
00:13:46,000 --> 00:13:47,040
Was it you?

174
00:13:49,640 --> 00:13:51,240
You gave me shares of Yuanmeng

175
00:13:52,640 --> 00:13:54,120
to confuse me,

176
00:13:54,560 --> 00:13:55,640
so that I would let my guard down

177
00:13:55,640 --> 00:13:57,360
and trust you with the project.

178
00:14:01,080 --> 00:14:01,920
Lin Moqing,

179
00:14:04,680 --> 00:14:06,720
