180
00:14:14,240 --> 00:14:15,200
Say it!

181
00:14:16,480 --> 00:14:18,240
You're always so eloquent.

182
00:14:18,240 --> 00:14:18,960
Speak up!
Are you mute?

183
00:14:21,120 --> 00:14:21,920
I admit,

184
00:14:28,240 --> 00:14:30,000
I did use you before,

185
00:14:32,400 --> 00:14:33,760
but I regret it now.

186
00:14:36,160 --> 00:14:38,120
I was blinded by hatred at that time.

187
00:14:40,240 --> 00:14:41,040
I'm sorry.

188
00:14:43,040 --> 00:14:43,560
Mengmeng,

189
00:14:44,440 --> 00:14:45,760
can you give me another chance?

190
00:14:46,040 --> 00:14:47,040
Lin Moqing,

191
00:14:51,440 --> 00:14:52,680
